normal cards:
    per color:
        4 basic (2 symbols, 3 open corners)
        3 points (1 symbol, 3 corners, 1 point)
        3 special (1 symbol, 1 other symbol, 1 special symbol, 3 corners)
        = 10 cards
    = 40 cards

gold cards:
    per color:
        1 5_point (2 corners, 5 points, req: 5 symbols), *for each color different side of corners
        3 3_point (2 corners, 1 special symbol, 3 points, req: 3 symbols)
        3 2_point (3 corners, 2 points per corner, req: 3 symbols; 1 other symbol)
        3 1_point (3 corners, 1 point per special symbol, 1 special symbol, req: 2 symbols; 1 other symbol)
        = 10 cards
    = 40 cards
= 80 cards

starting cards: either (4 corners, all 4 symbols)
                2 have 1 symbol, 4 corners, 2 symbols (1 same as middle)
                2 have 2 symbols, 4 corners
                2 have 3 symbols, 2 corners

objectives:
        3 points: all 3 special symbols
                  patterns 2 same color under each + 1 on side different

        2 points: 4 diagonal of 3 of same color
                  4 three same symbols
                  3 two of special symbols



sources:
 https://fonts.google.com/selection?preview.script=Latn